{"word":"G3654 - ὅλως - hólōs - hol'-oce - At all","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ὅλως</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">hólōs</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">hol'-oce</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">At all</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Adverb / வினையடை</span>"},{"paragraph":"பிரசித்தமாய், எவ்விதத்திலும், ஒருபோதும் - வினையடை"},{"paragraph":"wholly, altogether"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>Adverb from <a href=\"#/G3650 - ὅλος - hólos - hol'-os/3650\">G3650</a>; <i>completely</i>, that is, <i>altogether</i>; (by analogy) <i>everywhere</i>; (negative) not <i>by any means:</i> - at all, commonly, utterly.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}